TI  - Nutrient availability in soil samples from shifting cultivation sites in the semi-arid Caatinga of NE Brazil
T2  - AGRICULTURE ECOSYSTEMS & ENVIRONMENT
KW  - oxisol
KW  - subtractive fertilizer trial
KW  - additive fertilizer trial
